Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,額頭還疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…還有點疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我都嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼昨晚不好好睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次見小優接不到球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓姐姐輔導我學習到很晚才睡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想在下次的期中考試裡拿滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後嚇春香一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別勉強自己嘛  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你讓我擔心了  所以要受罰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還有人睡在旁邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  悄悄地來一下就好  悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家都受傷了  你有沒有搞清楚情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個聲音  是優嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別一個人嘀咕了  沒事了的話就快回去上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福連姐姐也睡眠不足了呢  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,親戚家的惠姐姐的婚禮是下個禮拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穿什麼衣服去好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了白色以外都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校服不也挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  爸爸那天要出差來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不你叫一個學校的朋友一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎  那我就叫小優
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和小雫  琴音  柚子  還有小楓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.25,zhushi2,NTP,0,0,0,,帶不了那麼多人的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就問問小優看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚嗎…我們家春香也差不多該是時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會讓那些來歷不明的臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰我家春香一根汗毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說爸爸啊  好像在說電視劇台詞一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說女孩子的話就沒問題了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.56,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}「櫻色的婚禮」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.56,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}「櫻色的婚禮」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小優  在睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下週要不要和我…婚禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…？那個不是還要辦些手續嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再說春香的父母也同意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  他們同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春…春香你覺得行的話我也沒問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  謝謝你小優
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我晚點再打給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要和春香結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香覺得這樣沒問題嗎  就這麼乾脆地…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都是女孩子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我還不知道在婚禮上要做些什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  優
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事沒辦法跟姐姐商量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不說  也總有一天會被她知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香也太突然了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算…算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛  剛才開始就欲言又止的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…要是兩個女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不該問這種多餘的問題的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  還是關於剛才說的那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穿校服去怎麼樣  雖然也可以去租禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來還可以穿校服進行婚禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我覺得既然這是一輩子的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是租一套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  小優也說想穿禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穿校服不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,租禮服最便宜也要五千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候就從春香的零花錢裡扣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,零花錢和小優的晚禮服…要選的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是要穿禮服啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？就這麼想穿嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1815,300)}一\N週\N後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,婚禮前的拜父母的環節好像還沒做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  你很緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  小優  不用這麼緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小女子不才  以後還請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  請多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是婚禮現場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是春香的玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來這裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是來租婚禮穿的禮服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:06:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是要結婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優石化了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優好可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  紺藍色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是純白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想選其他樣子的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這件也很合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優有化過妝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我自己來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就我也塗上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要在發誓時才親的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是很重要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優覺得自己是要進行誓約之吻的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們是要去給新娘子送上祝福的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會誤會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪春香你用那種奇怪的說話方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道春香就不想跟我結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就是誓約之吻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是誓約之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊嗯…準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那小優我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢把視線對上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來有請新人入場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請各位鼓掌歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候你爸估計也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這哭得也太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請切開結婚蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是抹茶味的就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抹茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  小優
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是對在這麼感人的場景下也只想到食物的春香感到有點遺憾罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真擔心以後的生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優居然被感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來將扔花束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家踴躍參與
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去接吧  小優
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  請開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  往這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  我拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人生會有第二春嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,惠姐姐  恭喜你結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…春香  謝謝你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回就輪到我參加你的婚禮了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得那一天不會遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請拿一些花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要撒花瓣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次撒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新娘真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  烤雞也很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕也很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙拉也很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家還在感慨著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感…感慨些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要結婚對象不是那些來路不明的臭小子就都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(375,780)}※才沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  幹嘛突然蹭過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
